divs: Sighting Detailsi was taking photos of san diego skyline, while driving over the bridge on harbor drive east. when i got home and examined them ,we noticed some specks on the photos horizons. i cropped pictre # 1498 and in doing so i lost the original picture. However , i do have # 1499 (the next picture taken in the series). it too, has evidence of ufo objects. Zoom in on the specks over the palm trees in the middle of the picture, and, zoom in on the specks on the lower right quadrant of the photo as well.
Summary: taking photos of san diego skyline while driving, upon close examination notice ufo's in pictures
